Do you trust me?Four words that can ask so much.When Jenifer Taylor met Aiden O’Connell - the billionaire Vice President of Mornington Vale’s largest financial corporation - she never thought she’d be forced to make a choice between trust and love. To love is easy. But to trust someone, when your world has been full of one disappointment after another, is not an easy task. When Aiden is investigated for a serious crime, can Jeni find the strength within to trust in his innocence? Can you ever genuinely trust in someone, especially if they claim they’re innocent?